297
00:20:28,759 --> 00:20:29,920
[Mr. Fan's definitely not part]

298
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:31,359
[of some amateur circus act.]

299
00:20:31,759 --> 00:20:33,920
[If Zhikun is the rising star among]

300
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:35,240
[Hang City's young lawyers,]

301
00:20:35,720 --> 00:20:37,519
[Mr. Fan and Dingzheng are]

302
