[Other than the high fees,]

304
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:41,319
[no flaws at all.]

305
00:20:43,079 --> 00:20:43,799
Simply put,

306
00:20:43,799 --> 00:20:45,079
this case is about

307
00:20:45,079 --> 00:20:46,920
proving your outline was stolen.

308
00:20:47,440 --> 00:20:49,160
Then can we compare

309
00:20:49,160 --> 00:20:50,680
