313
00:20:54,960 --> 00:20:56,559
and prove that my work is original

314
00:20:56,680 --> 00:20:57,440
and didn't infringe?

315
00:20:58,759 --> 00:21:00,039
That approach is pretty difficult

316
00:21:00,039 --> 00:21:00,960
