It might not work in your favor.

320
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:07,079
Proving the outline was stolen

321
00:21:07,079 --> 00:21:08,759
is the most direct and simplest way.

322
00:21:09,640 --> 00:21:10,920
I understand all that.

323
00:21:11,200 --> 00:21:12,079
But honestly,
the two works just

324
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:14,000
look a bit similar.

325
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:15,160
As an original author,

326
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:16,680
I want the legal recognition.

327
00:21:17,519 --> 00:21:18,440
Miss Ruan, sorry,

328
