331
00:21:27,559 --> 00:21:28,039
Understood.

332
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:34,559
[Miss Ruan,]

333
00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:35,920
[just a friendly heads-up,]

334
00:21:36,400 --> 00:21:37,720
[I don't think any lawyer]

335
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:38,759
