345
00:22:19,319 --> 00:22:20,079
[You're really not gonna sue?]

346
00:22:21,599 --> 00:22:22,200
Mr. Liu,

347
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:24,000
how would you

348
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:25,039
