if it were up to you?

349
00:22:26,440 --> 00:22:27,480
Prove the outline was stolen.

350
00:22:28,119 --> 00:22:29,440
That's the simplest way.

351
00:22:32,319 --> 00:22:32,839
What's wrong?

352
00:22:33,799 --> 00:22:34,920
Running into some trouble?

353
00:22:35,480 --> 00:22:36,720
You can tell me.

354
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:38,640
Even if I'm not your lawyer,

355
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:40,000
