of my work in this case.

359
00:22:48,799 --> 00:22:50,119
That's actually...

360
00:22:55,920 --> 00:22:56,799
It's okay, Mr. Liu.
I understand.

361
00:22:59,079 --> 00:22:59,559
Yes.

362
00:23:01,000 --> 00:23:01,720
Yes?

363
00:23:04,160 --> 00:23:05,359
Mr. Liu, if you're just doing this

364
00:23:05,359 --> 00:23:06,519
