366
00:23:08,319 --> 00:23:09,039
I know...

367
00:23:09,119 --> 00:23:10,079
Of course not.
It's no trouble.

368
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:13,279
Not at all.

369
00:23:17,640 --> 00:23:18,960
Are you on speaker,

370
00:23:18,960 --> 00:23:19,440
Mr. Liu?

371
00:23:20,480 --> 00:23:20,880
Yeah.

372
00:23:21,440 --> 00:23:22,359
Sorry about that, Ruan Yu.

373
00:23:22,599 --> 00:23:23,359
Hold on a sec.

374
00:23:24,240 --> 00:23:25,359
I need to sign two documents.

375
00:23:26,400 --> 00:23:26,839
Okay.

376
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:33,720
Any instructions?

377
00:23:51,839 --> 00:23:53,279
Proving your originality

378
00:23:53,759 --> 00:23:55,319
isn't essential evidence,

379
00:23:55,799 --> 00:23:56,920
but as supporting evidence,

380
00:23:58,839 --> 00:24:00,279
it may have a positive impact

381
00:24:00,279 --> 00:24:01,440
