385
00:24:11,920 --> 00:24:12,519
Hold on.

386
00:24:13,279 --> 00:24:14,880
Two more documents to sign.

387
00:24:17,440 --> 00:24:17,880
Okay.

388
00:24:23,440 --> 00:24:24,680
In this country, the easiest way

389
00:24:24,799 --> 00:24:25,680
to handle this kind of case

390
00:24:25,920 --> 00:24:27,920
is to go with the stolen outline angle.

391
00:24:28,279 --> 00:24:29,920
Different playbook from

392
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:30,640
