397
00:24:40,759 --> 00:24:41,319
What do you mean?

398
00:24:42,799 --> 00:24:44,039
Mr. Liu, are you still there?

399
00:24:44,599 --> 00:24:46,000
If you're busy,

400
00:24:46,319 --> 00:24:47,839
