Thank you so much, Mr. Liu.

409
00:25:20,160 --> 00:25:21,519
No worries. Goodbye.

410
00:25:29,559 --> 00:25:30,759
You can't take this case this way.

411
00:25:31,119 --> 00:25:32,119
You are

412
00:25:32,119 --> 00:25:33,160
