419
00:25:54,400 --> 00:25:56,039
Why go through all this trouble?

420
00:25:56,039 --> 00:25:57,359
You could've just told me.

421
00:25:59,599 --> 00:26:00,759
You know what,

422
00:26:02,119 --> 00:26:02,640
Ruan Yu

423
00:26:03,279 --> 00:26:04,720
