434
00:26:29,680 --> 00:26:30,519
Dinner tonight?

435
00:26:30,920 --> 00:26:31,319
No.

436
00:26:31,599 --> 00:26:32,359
Where you off to then?

437
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:35,400
Su City.

438
00:26:41,359 --> 00:26:42,000
Good, don't eat.

439
00:26:42,680 --> 00:26:43,480
Work meeting

440
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:44,519
