441
00:26:51,039 --> 00:26:52,640
Miss Ruan, see you tonight.

442
00:26:57,559 --> 00:26:58,680
A writer and a lawyer.

443
00:26:59,079 --> 00:27:00,279
That'd make a nice story.

444
00:27:02,160 --> 00:27:02,680
Has a nice ring to it.

445
00:27:04,079 --> 00:27:06,000
Huaisong, you're back?

446
