Okay. It's a deal.

456
00:27:34,720 --> 00:27:35,880
See you after school.

457
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:36,519
Love you.

458
00:27:43,519 --> 00:27:44,079
What a coincidence.

459
00:27:44,759 --> 00:27:45,599
