469
00:28:12,119 --> 00:28:12,960
Say that again!

470
00:28:13,319 --> 00:28:13,920
Looks like you've got
too much allowance!

471
00:28:16,400 --> 00:28:17,640
My luck

472
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:18,799
