475
00:28:24,960 --> 00:28:25,359
Who?

476
00:28:26,000 --> 00:28:26,880
Huaisong.

477
00:28:28,279 --> 00:28:29,240
A really handsome guy.

478
00:28:29,240 --> 00:28:30,759
Second only to Shican.

479
00:28:30,960 --> 00:28:32,279
Good-looking and rich.

480
00:28:32,359 --> 00:28:35,079
And he spends money on me.

481
00:28:45,319 --> 00:28:45,839
Huaisong!

482
00:28:47,839 --> 00:28:48,640
I'm such a space case.
Gotta go back.

483
00:28:56,640 --> 00:28:57,599
What's Shi doing?

484
00:28:59,720 --> 00:29:00,559
