488
00:29:07,359 --> 00:29:09,279
You're Shi's classmate?

489
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:11,839
We're buddies.

490
00:29:12,359 --> 00:29:13,200
Not just classmates.

491
00:29:13,720 --> 00:29:14,839
Not just classmates?

492
00:29:15,480 --> 00:29:16,359
Then who are you to her?

493
00:29:16,599 --> 00:29:17,440
What's it to you?

494
00:29:19,359 --> 00:29:21,039
You're trying to pump me

495
00:29:21,480 --> 00:29:22,680
