499
00:29:27,839 --> 00:29:28,519
You?

500
00:29:30,039 --> 00:29:31,240
You're that

501
00:29:32,279 --> 00:29:33,200
good-looking, rich guy

502
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:34,480
who spends money on her,

503
00:29:36,240 --> 00:29:36,720
