like that?

505
00:29:39,920 --> 00:29:40,799
It's just money.
Anyone can have it.

506
00:29:42,799 --> 00:29:43,359
Let me tell you,

507
00:29:45,759 --> 00:29:47,359
if you keep messing

508
00:29:47,720 --> 00:29:48,480
with Xu Huaishi,

509
00:29:50,559 --> 00:29:51,480
