Huaisong.

510
00:29:54,319 --> 00:29:55,319
You're still here?

511
00:29:57,160 --> 00:29:58,200
This is my classmate I told you about,

512
00:29:58,200 --> 00:29:59,160
Zhao Yi.

513
00:29:59,559 --> 00:30:00,599
