518
00:30:10,920 --> 00:30:11,480
Zhao Yi!

519
00:30:14,160 --> 00:30:16,079
What did you tell Huaisong?

520
00:30:17,680 --> 00:30:21,240
Shouldn't "Huaisong" be his last name?

521
00:30:23,279 --> 00:30:24,400
So I'd be Ms. Shi?

522
00:30:24,720 --> 00:30:26,960
He's Xu Huaisong, my real brother.

523
00:30:26,960 --> 00:30:27,680
Got a problem with that?

524
00:30:29,880 --> 00:30:31,319
No problem. Xu.

525
00:30:35,160 --> 00:30:35,680
Xu.

526
00:30:37,440 --> 00:30:38,480
I've got work tonight.

527
00:30:38,559 --> 00:30:39,359
Not joining you for dinner.

528
00:30:46,319 --> 00:30:46,880
Mr. Liu,
your friend is already here.

529
00:30:47,799 --> 00:30:48,640
I'll show you over.

530
00:30:48,920 --> 00:30:49,480
Okay. Thanks.

531
00:31:11,720 --> 00:31:13,519
Weren't you going to Su City?

532
00:31:14,559 --> 00:31:15,720
Back so soon?

533
00:31:25,039 --> 00:31:27,400
Shouldn't "Huaisong" be his last name?

534
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:28,839
Is Mr. Liu serious
this time?

535
00:31:29,799 --> 00:31:30,799
That shirt is expensive.

536
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:32,160
I never saw him wear it.

537
00:31:32,720 --> 00:31:33,440
Who is it?

538
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:34,680
Do I know this girl?

539
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:36,480
It's Miss Ruan, the one

540
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:37,319
