541
00:31:37,599 --> 00:31:38,799
Mr. Liu drew up the contract this afternoon.

542
00:31:39,039 --> 00:31:39,839
He's securing it tonight.

543
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:41,079
Securing the deal

544
00:31:41,079 --> 00:31:42,559
