547
00:32:18,880 --> 00:32:19,960
Mr. Liu?

548
00:32:23,559 --> 00:32:24,039
Yes.

549
00:32:25,920 --> 00:32:27,039
So we'll move forward

550
00:32:27,039 --> 00:32:28,240
with the plan we discussed on the phone,

551
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:28,640
right?

552
00:32:29,119 --> 00:32:29,720
Of course.

553
00:32:30,799 --> 00:32:31,799
We'll provide legal advice

554
00:32:31,799 --> 00:32:32,839
