555
00:32:32,839 --> 00:32:33,480
Never against
the client's wishes.

556
00:32:36,839 --> 00:32:37,359
That's great.

557
00:32:37,720 --> 00:32:39,079
I trust your expertise, Mr. Liu.

558
00:32:40,079 --> 00:32:41,599
Let's sign the contract then.

559
00:32:43,640 --> 00:32:44,400
Now?

560
00:32:50,880 --> 00:32:51,319
No rush.

561
00:32:53,680 --> 00:32:55,160
The contract can wait a few days.

562
00:32:56,359 --> 00:32:57,720
As for the online buzz,

563
00:32:58,160 --> 00:32:59,119
