567
00:33:04,920 --> 00:33:05,359
No.
This can't wait.

568
00:33:07,119 --> 00:33:08,279
The longer the buzz keeps building,

569
00:33:08,279 --> 00:33:09,720
the more risk we take on.

570
00:33:10,680 --> 00:33:11,160
Ruan Yu,

571
00:33:11,400 --> 00:33:12,759
