572
00:33:12,759 --> 00:33:14,039
Ask me if anything's unclear.

573
00:33:14,039 --> 00:33:14,759
No need to be formal.

574
00:33:15,119 --> 00:33:15,720
I've already signed
both copies.

575
00:33:17,319 --> 00:33:17,720
Okay.

576
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:23,599
I don't have any questions.

577
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:30,680
Great.

578
00:33:32,759 --> 00:33:33,279
Mr. Liu.

579
00:33:34,039 --> 00:33:34,640
If I file a lawsuit,

580
00:33:34,640 --> 00:33:35,960
what documents do I need to prepare?

581
00:33:36,839 --> 00:33:37,680
The priority

582
00:33:38,200 --> 00:33:39,680
is to get notarized copies

583
00:33:39,680 --> 00:33:41,599
of all the defamatory content

584
00:33:41,759 --> 00:33:42,640
about you online

585
00:33:42,640 --> 00:33:43,880
as soon as possible.

586
00:33:44,240 --> 00:33:44,960
I'll help you with that.

587
00:33:45,799 --> 00:33:47,079
Also, don't let anyone know

588
00:33:47,079 --> 00:33:48,160
you're planning to sue yet,

589
00:33:48,279 --> 00:33:49,400
or you might tip them off.

590
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:50,640
As for the rest...
Hold on.

591
00:33:53,240 --> 00:33:54,000
Mr. Liu,

592
00:33:54,200 --> 00:33:55,200
aren't you my counsel?

593
00:33:56,359 --> 00:33:57,160
Mr. Xu,

594
00:33:58,640 --> 00:33:59,559
are you involved too?

595
00:34:00,799 --> 00:34:02,119
Mr. Liu handles the court appearances.

596
00:34:02,880 --> 00:34:03,759
I'll help with case prep.

597
00:34:07,240 --> 00:34:09,440
But I can't afford

598
00:34:09,440 --> 00:34:10,280
to pay

599
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:11,519
two lawyers.

600
00:34:11,920 --> 00:34:12,760
Don't worry about that.

601
00:34:13,079 --> 00:34:14,119
He's just learning.

602
00:34:14,119 --> 00:34:15,079
You don't need to pay him.

603
00:34:15,519 --> 00:34:16,800
Besides, with our connection,

604
00:34:17,320 --> 00:34:18,400
I can give you 20% off.

605
00:34:19,280 --> 00:34:20,199
Thank you, Mr. Liu.

606
00:34:23,039 --> 00:34:23,639
Actually,

607
00:34:24,519 --> 00:34:26,320
I have a few friends in the industry

608
00:34:26,320 --> 00:34:27,960
who've been in copyright disputes.

609
00:34:28,519 --> 00:34:29,599
Mr. Xu, I could refer you to them

610
00:34:29,599 --> 00:34:30,800
if you want to study.

611
00:34:32,519 --> 00:34:33,519
I don't mind.

612
00:34:37,119 --> 00:34:38,119
Mr. Liu, is that okay with you?

613
00:34:52,559 --> 00:34:53,920
After all, this isn't

614
00:34:53,920 --> 00:34:55,039
a Zhikun case.

615
00:34:55,559 --> 00:34:56,360
So if Mr. Xu
gets involved,

616
00:34:57,320 --> 00:35:00,119
it might not look great for the firm,

617
00:35:04,239 --> 00:35:04,760
right?

618
00:35:10,760 --> 00:35:11,360
Mr. Xu,

619
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:12,880
when you say

620
00:35:12,880 --> 00:35:14,320
"help with case prep,"

621
00:35:15,840 --> 00:35:17,400
does that mean you'll advise

622
00:35:17,760 --> 00:35:18,719
Mr. Liu on strategy,

623
00:35:19,280 --> 00:35:20,679
but not handle everything...

624
00:35:20,679 --> 00:35:21,760
The first step of case prep

625
00:35:22,719 --> 00:35:24,079
is fully understanding the case.

626
00:35:25,159 --> 00:35:26,239
So you have to

627
00:35:26,239 --> 00:35:26,960
review all the documents?

628
00:35:27,360 --> 00:35:28,760
Including the entire novel?

629
00:35:31,039 --> 00:35:32,280
Miss Ruan, is there something

630
00:35:33,480 --> 00:35:34,360
in your novel
you'd rather not share?

631
00:35:38,559 --> 00:35:39,480
No, no.

632
00:35:41,960 --> 00:35:42,480
No.

633
00:35:44,400 --> 00:35:46,000
Alright. Contract's signed.

634
00:35:46,480 --> 00:35:48,239
Let me set up a work group chat.

635
00:35:48,760 --> 00:35:50,239
That way we can communicate easily.

636
00:35:50,760 --> 00:35:51,239
Alright?

637
00:35:52,559 --> 00:35:54,000
Sure.

638
00:36:02,519 --> 00:36:03,719
In 1,000 meters,

639
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:05,480
you'll get on the airport expressway.

640
00:36:54,119 --> 00:36:54,920
[Mr. Xu will handle]

641
00:36:54,920 --> 00:36:56,320
[organizing the plot points]

642
00:36:56,320 --> 00:36:57,320
[from the novel for our case.]

643
00:36:57,639 --> 00:36:58,280
[If you have any questions,]

644
00:36:59,039 --> 00:36:59,800
[feel free to reach out to him.]

645
00:37:06,119 --> 00:37:06,840
[Mr. Liu,]

646
00:37:06,880 --> 00:37:08,320
[for the plot organization part,]

647
00:37:08,440 --> 00:37:09,079
[can I just]
[coordinate with you?]

648
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:14,000
[Mr. Xu has more experience]

649
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:15,000
[with plagiarism checks.]

650
00:37:20,719 --> 00:37:21,760
[I just thought with Mr. Xu]

651
00:37:21,760 --> 00:37:22,800
[being overseas, the time difference]

652
00:37:22,880 --> 00:37:23,559
[would be a hassle.]

653
00:37:24,119 --> 00:37:26,000
[Plus, he's probably pretty busy.]

654
00:37:26,960 --> 00:37:28,119
[Don't worry about the time difference.]

655
00:37:28,480 --> 00:37:29,360
[He's a night owl.]

656
00:37:29,960 --> 00:37:31,039
[And no matter how busy he is,]

657
00:37:31,519 --> 00:37:32,960
[for my sake,]

658
00:37:33,199 --> 00:37:34,360
[he'll make time for this case.]

659
00:37:35,079 --> 00:37:36,119
[Once the materials are organized,]

660
00:37:36,119 --> 00:37:37,079
[you can post them in the group chat.]

661
00:37:59,719 --> 00:38:00,280
Hello?

662
00:38:03,199 --> 00:38:03,800
Man,

663
00:38:04,679 --> 00:38:05,880
this type of case

664
00:38:05,880 --> 00:38:07,519
is your specialty, right?

665
00:38:07,920 --> 00:38:09,920
You told me to say in the group chat

666
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:11,400
that you're handling this case.

667
00:38:11,400 --> 00:38:12,360
I did it.

668
00:38:12,440 --> 00:38:14,280
Then Ruan Yu responded,

669
00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:15,360
and you just went silent.

670
00:38:16,679 --> 00:38:17,519
What's your deal?

671
00:38:18,079 --> 00:38:18,760
You're putting me

672
00:38:18,760 --> 00:38:20,119
in a really tough spot here.

673
00:38:27,719 --> 00:38:28,760
If you're really that uncomfortable

674
00:38:28,760 --> 00:38:30,480
being in the middle,

675
00:38:31,159 --> 00:38:31,880
just come sit over here.

676
00:38:34,920 --> 00:38:35,440
Fine.

677
00:38:40,800 --> 00:38:41,440
You can have her

678
00:38:41,440 --> 00:38:42,559
add me on WeChat.

679
00:38:43,480 --> 00:38:44,559
I see now.

680
00:38:45,239 --> 00:38:46,960
You came back all of a sudden

681
00:38:47,079 --> 00:38:48,239
for Ruan Yu.

682
00:38:50,679 --> 00:38:51,679
Shi got into some trouble.

683
00:38:52,440 --> 00:38:53,320
That's a terrible excuse.

684
00:38:53,960 --> 00:38:54,719
Seriously?

685
00:38:55,639 --> 00:38:57,079
If you have time to gossip,

686
00:38:57,360 --> 00:38:58,280
why not just have the client
contact me?

687
00:38:59,840 --> 00:39:00,599
Wait.

688
00:39:01,400 --> 00:39:02,559
Why do you want her

689
00:39:02,559 --> 00:39:03,119
to contact you?

690
00:39:05,679 --> 00:39:06,960
Don't tell me you added her

691
00:39:07,360 --> 00:39:08,840
and she didn't accept?

692
00:39:08,840 --> 00:39:09,760
Nonsense.

693
00:39:11,480 --> 00:39:12,360
So I guessed right!

694
00:39:16,519 --> 00:39:18,079
Looks like you've got more experience

695
00:39:18,840 --> 00:39:20,239
being rejected than I do, Mr. Liu.

696
00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:23,679
You got anything or not?
If not, I'm hanging up.

697
00:39:26,079 --> 00:39:27,000
I'll hang up first.

698
00:39:32,079 --> 00:39:33,280
I've got more experience?

699
00:40:13,880 --> 00:40:15,000
[Here's the defamation record]

700
00:40:15,000 --> 00:40:15,719
[I've organized so far.]

701
00:40:16,119 --> 00:40:17,800
[I already had it notarized]

702
00:40:17,800 --> 00:40:18,880
[at the notary office this morning.]

703
00:40:19,519 --> 00:40:20,840
[Please take a look and let me know]

704
00:40:20,840 --> 00:40:21,960
[if anything else needs to be added.]

705
00:40:33,119 --> 00:40:34,599
[You should add him on WeChat.]

706
00:40:34,599 --> 00:40:35,760
[He's in too many work group chats.]

707
00:40:35,760 --> 00:40:36,960
[Might miss things sometimes.]

708
00:40:44,000 --> 00:40:45,800
Add Xu Huaisong on WeChat?

709
00:41:03,159 --> 00:41:05,119
4308.

710
00:41:26,880 --> 00:41:28,320
[Back then, I spent three years]

711
00:41:28,320 --> 00:41:29,519
[going over his info]

712
00:41:29,880 --> 00:41:31,280
[and never found a reason to add him.]

713
00:41:32,199 --> 00:41:34,320
[Ten years later, here it is.]

714
00:41:36,119 --> 00:41:36,800
[Life really has]

715
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:38,000
[a twisted sense of humor.]

716
00:41:49,440 --> 00:41:50,440
What do I say?

717
00:41:52,599 --> 00:41:54,280
Hello, Mr. Xu.

718
00:41:54,880 --> 00:41:55,559
This is Ruan Yu.

719
00:41:57,239 --> 00:41:59,320
No. Too formal.

720
00:42:13,639 --> 00:42:14,280
No.

721
00:42:15,119 --> 00:42:16,239
Too stiff.

722
00:42:22,119 --> 00:42:23,320
What do I do?

723
00:42:24,920 --> 00:42:26,719
No! I can't add him!

724
00:42:27,840 --> 00:42:29,440
Talking to him about the novel

725
00:42:29,440 --> 00:42:30,400
feels too awkward

726
00:42:30,679 --> 00:42:31,719
What if I slip up?

727
00:42:59,960 --> 00:43:01,599
[A young lady with no legal background]

728
00:43:01,599 --> 00:43:03,400
[would rather figure out]

729
00:43:03,400 --> 00:43:05,000
[notarization herself]

730
00:43:05,280 --> 00:43:06,119
[than let you help.]

731
00:43:06,440 --> 00:43:07,280
[Looks like she really doesn't]
[want to deal with you.]

732
00:43:18,000 --> 00:43:20,400
How... Did I just add him?

733
00:43:21,000 --> 00:43:21,519
What...

734
00:43:22,159 --> 00:43:23,440
What did my friend request

735
00:43:23,440 --> 00:43:24,159
say?

736
00:43:52,360 --> 00:43:52,840
Have a seat.

737
00:43:57,880 --> 00:43:58,800
One more thing.

738
00:43:59,360 --> 00:44:00,480
Someone

739
00:44:01,039 --> 00:44:02,599
found a phone in the auditorium.

740
00:44:03,599 --> 00:44:05,519
Is anyone here to claim it?

741
00:44:09,079 --> 00:44:09,840
Nobody?

742
00:44:13,199 --> 00:44:14,000
Whose phone is this?

743
00:44:19,400 --> 00:44:20,400
The "study or marry me"

744
00:44:20,880 --> 00:44:22,159
person,

745
00:44:23,039 --> 00:44:23,639
come up

746
00:44:23,639 --> 00:44:24,840
and get your phone.

747
00:44:31,440 --> 00:44:32,119
Whose phone?

748
00:44:35,880 --> 00:44:37,280
Sir. Sir.

749
00:44:37,360 --> 00:44:38,000
Sir, I'm sorry.

750
00:44:38,760 --> 00:44:39,400
It's mine.

751
00:44:39,880 --> 00:44:40,440
Don't bring

752
00:44:40,440 --> 00:44:41,679
your phone to school anymore.

753
00:44:42,840 --> 00:44:43,840
Focus on your studies.

754
00:44:45,320 --> 00:44:46,400
Thank you, sir. Sorry about that.
